description.en:
Calling • Ability • Precondition: Confessor or Dreamtender You are well trained in watching for small details in expression and body language;
                you can often tell if someone is being deceitful. Benefice: When someone attempts to confuse or deceive you, roll a d20: 1-10 = the roll is
                unfavorable; 11-20 = the roll is unaffected by your training.
